# Swift AppCore NativeUi ABI smoke

[signal, textNode, signalText, fragment, emit](../../runtime/std/ui/primitives.ssc)

```scalascript
val message = signal("message", "before")
message.set("after")

emit(
  fragment([textNode(message.id), signalText(message)]),
  "/tmp/ssc-nativeui"
)
```
